#id=1
#text=Last Friday , I took an airplane flight to New York for a business trip .
#id=2
#text=About two weeks before the trip , I went online and determined which airlines flew to New York , and how much it cost for each flight .
#id=3
#text=After looking at all the possible flights , I decided to take the morning jetBlue flight , which was also the cheapest .
#id=4
#text=I bought the ticket online with my credit card , and printed out a boarding pass on my printer .
#id=5
#text=On Friday morning , I got up before sunrise and showered , then packed the items I would need for the trip into my small travel bag .
#id=6
#text=I had just a few minutes to make a cup of coffee , then drove to the airport .
#id=7
#text=I parked in the parking garage , then made my way to the terminal .
#id=8
#text=First , I checked the flight information board to see if my flight was on-time , which it was , and to find the departure gate .
#id=9
#text=Then I proceeded to security , waited in line , and then after clearing security , went to the boarding gate .
#text=I waited for only ten minutes , and they called for general boarding , so into the line I went , and the gate agent scanned my boarding pass as I entered the jetway .
#text=I was greeted by an attendant as I entered the plane , and I slowly made my way down the aisle to my seat , 16A .
#text=After stowing my bag in the overhead bin , I sat in my seat and buckled up .
#text=Soon after that , the door closed , we pushed back from the gate and the engines spooled up .
#text=We were in the air within 5 minutes , climbing to 35,000 feet through the clouds .
#text=I was able to get a cup of coffee during the short flight , and within 30 minutes , we were already beginning out descent .
#text=The attendant collected the empty coffee cup , and soon after we were touching down .
#text=It was a quick ride to the gate , seat belts off , and everybody got up , grabbing their luggage .
#text=After a slow crawl up the aisle , and a quick goodbye to the crew , I was out of the plane , walking up the jetway and out to the arrival gate .
#text=All in all , it was a pleasant flight .
